# agentic-core — symlink target
# On the VPS (Linux), create a symlink from packages/agentic_core to the
# agentic-core repo:
#
#   ln -s /home/evans/Tools/agentic-core packages/agentic_core
#
# On macOS:
#   ln -s /path/to/agentic-core packages/agentic_core
#
# On Windows (elevated PowerShell):
#   New-Item -ItemType Junction -Path packages\agentic_core -Target C:\path\to\agentic-core
#
# This path is gitignored (see .gitignore). Set it up once per machine.
